{
  "_doc": "Layer 0 共享巨集表（單一真相源）。reader 經 build/gen_macros.py codegen 注入 mathJaxConfig.tex.macros；驗證器 render_check.js 編成 \\def preamble。寬鬆策略：真數學符號展開成 unicode、文字排版命令 best-effort、accent 近似。故意不收 OCR 黏字偽巨集（\\Nu \\muA \\cdotE…）與 delimiter 殘體（\\] \\(）——定義會掩蓋真錯，留 Layer 2 上報 / Layer 3 sweep。值為 string（無參）或 [body, nargs]（有參）。需要 reader 載 unicode + enclose 套件。",
  "macros": {
    "\\AA": "{\\unicode{xC5}}",
    "\\aa": "{\\unicode{xE5}}",
    "\\dag": "{\\dagger}",
    "\\ddag": "{\\ddagger}",
    "\\hdots": "{\\cdots}",
    "\\oiint": "{\\unicode{x222F}}",
    "\\oiiint": "{\\unicode{x2230}}",
    "\\pounds": "{\\unicode{xA3}}",
    "\\P": "{\\unicode{xB6}}",
    "\\astrosun": "{\\unicode{x2609}}",
    "\\llbracket": "{\\unicode{x27E6}}",
    "\\rrbracket": "{\\unicode{x27E7}}",
    "\\llangle": "{\\unicode{x27EA}}",
    "\\rrangle": "{\\unicode{x27EB}}",
    "\\dprime": "{\\unicode{x2033}}",
    "\\nsimeq": "{\\unicode{x2244}}",
    "\\joinrel": "\\mathrel{\\mkern-3mu}",
    "\\thickspace": "{\\;}",
    "\\allowbreak": "{}",
    "\\harpoonleft": "{\\leftharpoonup}",
    "\\sp": "^",
